One should note that many of the promises given at Luz are currently being realized while Jacob’s family is in Egypt. In Egypt they are fertile (or “fruitful,” pārá, 47:27; 48:4). In Egypt they are numerous (or “multiplying,” rāḇá, 47:27; 48:4). In Egypt they are acquiring land as an everlasting holding (ʾḥz, 47:27; 48:4)   
